          "message": "Refactoring orthogonality and dualising covariance (#138)\n\n* Dfn: Orthogonality for families\n\n* Dualise covariance\n\n* Prf: exponentiating covariant families by contravariant families\n\n* Flips default direction of pullback associated to arrow map\n\n* Prf: Right Segal types are Segal\n\n* Add patterns for Δ¹ boundaries\n\n* Prf: Representables are contravariant iff type is right Segal\n\n* Add informal proof for exponentiating covariant families\n\n* Make explicit dependent and non-dependent extension types\n\n* Changelog\n\n* Apply suggestions from code review\n\nCo-authored-by: Fredrik Bakke <fredrbak@gmail.com>\n\n* Type families\n\nCo-authored-by: Fredrik Bakke <fredrbak@gmail.com>\n\n* Contra -> contrav\n\n* Pullback stable -> Base change stable\n\n* leftmost\n\n* Fix typo\n\n* Changelog changes\n\n* Rename trees\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Fredrik Bakke <fredrbak@gmail.com>",
